{
  "key": "mm-aos-letter",
  "config": {
    "defaultStyle": {
      "font": "Cambay"
    },
    "content": [

      {
        "style": "noc-head",
        "table": {
          "widths": [
            50, "*"
          ],
          "body": [
            [{
                "image": "{{logo}}",
                "width": 50,
                "margin": [8, 10, 10, 0]
              },
              {
                "stack": [{
                  "text": "OFFICE OF THE ADDITIONAL COMMISSIONER-I, SUB OFFICE, MANIMAJRA, MUNICIPAL CORPORATION, CHANDIGARH",
                  "style": "pt-reciept-citizen-header"
                }],
                "alignment": "center",
                "margin": [
                  0,
                  12,
                  0,
                  0
                ]
              }
            ]
          ]
        },
        "layout": "noBorders"
      },
      {
        "style": "pt-reciept-citizen-header",
        "columns": [{
            "width": "auto",
            "text": [{
                "text": "Memo No. ",
                "bold": true
              },
              {
                "text": "{{applicationNumber}}",
                "bold": false
              }
            ],
            "alignment": "left"
          },
          {
            "text": ""
          },
          {
            "width": "auto",
            "text": [{
                "text": "Dated ",
                "bold": true
              },
              {
                "text": "{{approvalDate}}",
                "bold": false
              }
            ],
            "alignment": "right"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "margin": [0, 20, 0, 0],
        "text": "To",
        "alignment": "left",
        "style": "pdfContent"
      },
      {
        "margin": [0, 10, 0, 0],
        "stack": [{
            "preserveLeadingSpaces": true,
            "text": "               {{name}}",
            "style": "pdfContent",
            "width": "*"
          },
          {
            "preserveLeadingSpaces": true,
            "text": "               {{address}}",
            "style": "pdfContent",
            "width": "*"
          }

        ]
      },
      {
        "margin": [0, 10, 0, 0],
        "columns": [{
            "text": "Sub:-",
            "style": "pdfContent",
            "bold": true,
            "width": "auto",
            "alignment": "left"

          },
          {
            "margin": [20, 0, 0, 0],
            "width": "*",
            "text": "Allotment of New House/Shop No. {{houseNumber}} Mohalla {{mohalla}} Manimajra",
            "style": "pdfContent",
            "bold": true
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "margin": [0, 20, 0, 0],
        "preserveLeadingSpaces": true,
        "style": "pdfContent",
        "text": "              Reference on the subject noted above."
      },
      {
        "margin": [0, 5, 0, 0],
        "style": "pdfContent",
        "text": [{
            "text": "In view of certified copy of sale deed Regd at Sr.No. "
          },
          {
            "text": "{{registrationNumber}}",
            "bold": true
          },
          {
            "text": " dated "
          },
          {
            "text": "{{submissionDate}}",
            "bold": true
          },
          {
            "text": " along with Indemnity Bond, affidavits, Site Plan Report of Halqa Patwari duly authenticated by the Tehsildar, U.T , Chandigarh. No Due Certificate regarding water charges, etc. submitted by you.House/shop No. "
          },
          {
            "text": "{{houseNumber}}",
            "bold": true
          },
          {
            "text": " Mohalla "
          },
          {
            "text": "{{mohalla}}",
            "bold": true
          },
          {
            "text": ", Manimajra area "
          },
          {
            "text": "{{areaSqft}}",
            "bold": true
          },
          {
            "text": " sq. Yds is hereby entered in your names on the following terms and conditions -"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "margin": [0, 20, 0, 0],
        "style": "pdfContent",
        "stack": [{
            "text": "1. That you will abide by the provisions of the The Chandigarh Administration (erection and re-erection of Buildings) Rules, 2006 for villages in the Municipal Corporation. Chandigarh' as notified on 27.12.2006 and as amended from time to time."
          },
          {
            "text": "2. If you want to make any alteration/modification/change in the existing super structure/building in the house, you shall be required to get the building plan sanctioned prior to commencement of construction / modifications / alteration in the building"
          },
          {
            "text": "3. In case, there is a cantilever, any projection which do not conform to the provisions of 'order dated 8.11.2006 issued on 16.11.2006 regarding minimum clear heignt or maximum allowed width or projection/encroachment upon government land, the same shall be modified/set aside at the time of addition and alteration in the super structure of the building. Otherwise any encroachment on public/Municipal land is liable tn he removed/demolished as per already existing policy of removal of encroachments"
          },
          {
            "text": "4. Any Financial liability or government dues payable to any department or agency or organization shall be payable by you. "
          },
          {
            "text": "5. You are hereby granted No Objection Certificate for Electricity, Water and Sewerage Connections for your above mentioned building."
          },
          {
            "text": "6. In case documents/ information submitted by you is found false/ incorrect at any later stage, the letter in question  shall be withdrawn/cancelled."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "alignment": "right",
        "margin": [0, 20, 0, 0],
        "style": "pdfContent",
        "bold": true,
        "stack": [{
            "text": " AC (F&A),"
          },
          {
            "text": "For Additional Commissioner-I, "
          },
          {
            "text": "Municipal Corporation, Chandigarh. "
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "margin": [0, 20, 10, 10],
        "columns": [{
            "text": "Endst No. MC/Addl.CMC/C-III/Manimajra/2021/",
            "style": "pdfContent",
            "alignment": "left",
            "bold": true
          },
          {
            "text": "Dated: ___________",
            "style": "pdfContent",
            "alignment": "right",
            "bold": true
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "stack": [{
            "preserveLeadingSpaces": true,
            "text": "           A copy is forwarded to the following for information and necessary action -  ",
            "style": "pdfContent"
          },
          {
            "text": "1.         1. The SDE, PH, Sub Div. No. 8, Manimajra, Municipal Corporation, Chandigarh",
            "style": "pdfContent",
            "preserveLeadingSpaces": true
          }
        ]
      }


    ],
    "styles": {
      "pdfContent": {
        "color": "#000000",
        "bold": false,
        "fontSize": 11,
        "fontWeight": 400,
        "margin": [
          3,
          0,
          0,
          0
        ]
      },
      "pt-reciept-citizen-header": {
        "fontSize": 12,
        "bold": true,
        "margin": [
          0,
          8,
          0,
          0
        ],
        "color": "#484848"
      },
      "receipt-logo-header": {
        "color": "#484848",
        "fontSize": 14,
        "bold": true,
        "letterSpacing": 0.74,
        "margin": [
          0,
          0,
          0,
          5
        ]
      },
      "receipt-logo-sub-header": {
        "color": "#484848",
        "fontFamily": "Roboto",
        "fontSize": 13,
        "letterSpacing": 1.6,
        "margin": [
          0,
          6,
          0,
          0
        ]
      },
      "noc-head": {
        "margin": [
          -25,
          -25,
          0,
          1
        ]
      }

    }
  }
}